<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Magazine Return Policy</span></p>
<p>U.S. and Canadian retailers may receive credit for unsold magazines for up to 6 months from the invoice date. A separate Affidavit Return Form will be provided for any publications received and that meet the returns criteria. Enter the quantity/quantities of unsold copies and simply email to: <a href="mailto:magreturns@kalmbach.com">magreturns@kalmbach.com</a> or fax to: 262-798-6543.</p></div>
    


